#!Paper paperClass Wiki Syntax
= Wiki Syntax =
Brief descriptions of AhaWiki Syntax
== Heading ==
[[[#!WikiSyntaxPreview
= h1
== h2 with closing ==
=== h3 with closing and id === #h3
==== h4
===== h5
====== h6
TOC is automatically generated when heading appears 5 or more.
]]]

----
== List
=== Ordered List
[[[#!WikiSyntaxPreview
 * bullet
  * bullet
   * bullet
  * bullet
  * bullet
 * bullet
]]]

=== Unordered List
[[[#!WikiSyntaxPreview
 1. decimal
 1. decimal
  I. ROMAN
  I. ROMAN
   A. ALPHA
   A. ALPHA
    i. roman
    i. roman
     a. alpha
     a. alpha
]]]

=== Mixed
[[[#!WikiSyntaxPreview
 * bullet
  1. decimal
  1. decimal
   * bullet
    A. Alpha
    A. Alpha
]]]

----
== Formatting ==
[[[#!WikiSyntaxPreview
 * ''italic''
 * '''bold'''
 * '''''bold italic'''''
 * __underline__
 * ~~strikeout~~
 * `code`
]]]


== Link
[[[#!WikiSyntaxPreview
 * Wiki Page
  1. [wiki:Page1] \[wiki:Escape]
  1. [wiki:Page1 Alias For Page1] \[wiki:Escape Escape]
 * Anchor - [#Anchor] [#Anchor Anchor Alias]
 * QueryString - [?q=10] [?q=10 q10 Alias]
 * Url
  1. http://aha00a.com
  1. [http://aha00a.com]
  1. [http://aha00a.com aha00a.com Alias]
]]]

----
== Macro
=== `Get`, `Set`
[[[#!WikiSyntaxPreview
[[Set(A,VAR_A)]]
[[Get(A)]] [[Get(A)]]
]]]

=== `Br`, `Html`, `Image`
[[[#!WikiSyntaxPreview
 * aaa[[Br]]bbb[[Br]]ccc
 * [[Html(<div style="border: 1px solid #f00">red border</div>)]]
 * [[Image(/public/favicon.png)]] [[Image(/public/favicon.png,16px)]]
]]]

